  <brief_title>A Comparison of XELOX Regimen and EOX Regimen as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy Regimen for Locally Advanced Gastric Cancer.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of XELOX Regimen and EOX Regimen as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy Regimen for Locally Advanced Gastric Cancer</official_title>
